EXPLAIN (COSTS OFF, STAT ON)
SELECT * FROM sc_a s1 JOIN sc_a s2 ON true
WHERE s1.x=1 AND s2.y LIKE 'a';
                                                     QUERY PLAN                                                      
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Nested Loop
   ->  Seq Scan on sc_a s1
         Filter: (x = 1)
   ->  Seq Scan on sc_a s2
         Filter: (y ~~ 'a'::text)
 Statistics:
   sc_a (s2).y: 1 times, stats: { MCV: 10 values, Correlation, ndistinct: 10.0000, nullfrac: 0.0000, width: 5 }
   sc_a (s1).x: 1 times, stats: { Histogram: 0 values, Correlation, ndistinct: -1.0000, nullfrac: 0.0000, width: 4 }
(8 rows)

